@MatrixRunSuffix = 20260403a
@MatrixWhitespaceEmail = matrix.whitespace.user.{{MatrixRunSuffix}}@example.com

#  ADMIN
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@AdminMechanicId = 2

### [Setup][Admin] Login as admin (session prerequisite)
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{AdminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{AdminPassword}}"
}

###

### [Positive][Admin] List all mechanics
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/mechanics

###

### [Negative][Admin] Try deleting self/admin mechanic (403 expected)
DELETE {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/mechanics/{{AdminMechanicId}}

###

# Set @AdminMechanicId to a non-admin mechanic id before running this positive case.
### [Positive][Admin] Delete non-admin mechanic
DELETE {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/mechanics/{{AdminMechanicId}}

###

### [Setup][Admin] Login as non-admin for forbidden access check
POST {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{MatrixWhitespaceEmail}}",
  "password": "{{TestPassword}}"
}

###

### [Negative][Admin] Non-admin cannot list mechanics (403 expected)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/mechanics
